{"id":476911,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":6,"day":30}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"工农兵纪念“七一”诗画选,歌唱共产党　歌唱毛主席","genre":"","count":"184","ytitle":"","mtitle":"《毛主席语录》发下来","ftitle":"","authors":["孙建华"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上钢三厂　孙建华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《毛主席语录》发下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限激情涌胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字句句闪金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的真理传万代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《毛主席语录》拿在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双臂猛增力万斤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷白大山一把推，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵着时代向前走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《毛主席语录》贴在胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身上下热血涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界风云收眼底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲四海装胸中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《毛主席语录》随身带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心红眼亮意志坚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远革命跟党走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举红旗奔向前!"}]}